CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 5, 1966, pg. 1B, reads: "Swing And Sway - One of the best looking couples on the dance floor was Mr. and Mrs. William Hawthorne. The photographer caught them as they glided around the ballroom. (All Teenie Harris photos)"
TitMainTitle: Gertrude and William Hawthorne dancing in ballroom of Roosevelt Hotel for Danettes Mardi Gras Ball
